Bobertron was on his way to see megatron when he was
called by magmatron. He said that he would benifit
more from his faction. This hit boberton's weak spot
greed. Bobertron thought for a moment. Him and
Megatron have been comrades for a long time. He was
the man who desabled the forc feild allowing him to
steal the golden disc. But magamatron had a good
sound. He decided to go with magamatron. How will this
afffect the outcome of this war.
